wishes.message: Happy B’Day to the most stylish girl. I hope your birthday is as beautiful as you. May your birthday be the happiest day ever. Always be happy & I'll do everything to make you so.
May your birthday be full of happy hours and special moments to cherish for a long long time. Enjoy your second quarantine Birthday. Many Many Happy Returns of the day.

Happiest Birthday Divyaa!!! I really miss talking about life with you!! Wish we spent more time together. I wish you receive all you desire ✨ You are literally my soul sister!!! You made me like baingan ka bharta, It was the tastiest!!!!
Whatever you ask may you receive, whatever you seek may you find, whatever you wish may it be fulfilled on your birthday and always. Happy Birthday Girawat!
Many many happy returns of the day Divya. Enjoy your day!!

Through you, I feel like my life of black & white and shades of grey turned into a colorful painting of life. So, instead of saying Happy Birthday from now on, I'm going to say "I am quite happy about your existence and I praise the day you were born." Today marks the birth date of a woman that has taught, inspired, and guided me towards becoming a better man. Always remember that there will always be me who watches and cares for you. Wishing all your dreams come true and all the good things will come through.
